  ('city:austria:vienna', 'city', 'vienna', 'vienna-lower-austria', 'Europe', 'Austria', 'Vienna', 'Vienna', 'Vienna is a polished cultural capital where imperial museums, coffeehouses, wine taverns, concert halls, design hotels, markets, and ring-road walks make a refined city break. It works best on foot, with landmarks as the spine and meals or neighborhood detours keeping it from feeling dutiful.'),
  ('neighborhood:austria:vienna:vienna:innere-stadt', 'neighborhood', 'innere-stadt', 'vienna', 'Europe', 'Austria', 'Vienna', 'Innere Stadt', 'Innere Stadt is Vienna''s imperial first district, where palaces, churches, museums, cafes, and shopping streets form the city''s most concentrated historic loop. It works best early or late, with one major cultural anchor and enough cafe time to keep the grandeur from feeling mechanical.'),
  ('neighborhood:austria:vienna:vienna:leopoldstadt', 'neighborhood', 'leopoldstadt', 'vienna', 'Europe', 'Austria', 'Vienna', 'Leopoldstadt', 'Leopoldstadt is Vienna''s island district, where Prater park, canals, markets, Jewish history, and newer food scenes give the city a looser eastern edge. It works best as a park-and-neighborhood route, especially when the center needs more air and less formality.'),
  ('neighborhood:austria:vienna:vienna:neubau', 'neighborhood', 'neubau', 'vienna', 'Europe', 'Austria', 'Vienna', 'Neubau', 'Neubau is Vienna''s design-forward seventh district, where MuseumsQuartier edges, indie shops, cafes, bars, and small galleries make the city feel younger. It works best from afternoon into evening, with browsing, museum time, and dinner kept within a tight grid.'),
  ('neighborhood:austria:vienna:vienna:mariahilf', 'neighborhood', 'mariahilf', 'vienna', 'Europe', 'Austria', 'Vienna', 'Mariahilf', 'Mariahilf is Vienna''s shopping-and-side-street district, where Mariahilfer Strasse, courtyards, cafes, theaters, and Naschmarkt edges keep plans practical. It works best as a flexible central route, using shopping or food as the anchor instead of chasing landmarks.'),
